title: Intensive Purposes (feat. Bobby Kelly)
description: Knowledge is power & no one will bash you over the head with it quite like Jay and Dan. Bobby Kelly joins the show and discusses the expectable sexual positions for the length challenged. Dan, Jay and Joe DeRosa marvel at Justin Silver’s access to the finer things in life.
